---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base";
import SocialList from "@/components/SocialList";
---

<PageLayout meta={{ title: "Portfolio" }}>
        <section>
                <h1 class="title mb-6">Professional Portfolio</h1>
                <p class="mb-4">
                        I bridge software, construction, and business at <strong>Uresco Construction Materials</strong>. My expertise combines full-stack development, system operations, business process optimization, Web3 development, and hands-on building knowledge to solve real-world problems in warehouse management, inventory, logistics, and sales.
                </p>
                <SocialList />
        </section>

        <div class="section-grid">
                <section class="mt-16">
                        <h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Areas of Expertise</h2>
                        <ul class="space-y-4">
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Full-Stack Web Development</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Building responsive, performant web applications with JavaScript/TypeScript, React, Astro, and Node.js. Creating interfaces that solve real business problems.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>System Operations & Infrastructure</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Infrastructure management, system architecture, deployment strategies, operational tools, and day-to-day operations that keep applications and business processes running reliably.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Business Process Optimization</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Improving warehouse, inventory, logistics, and sales workflows. Understanding business needs and creating software solutions that drive efficiency and growth.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Warehouse & Inventory Management</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Database design, inventory tracking, material management systems, supply chain optimization, and logistics solutions for the lumber and construction industry.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Web3 & Blockchain Development</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Hedera network development including dynamic NFTs, micro-payment systems, and tools that connect real-world activity to on-chain data. Smart contracts and decentralized applications for business innovation.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>3D Visualization & Geolocation</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Interactive 3D visualization tools using Three.js and WebGL, GPS tracking, mapping integrations, and real-time logistics applications.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Building & Construction</strong>
                                        <p class="mt-2">Hands-on experience in building and construction, lumber expertise, materials knowledge, and practical construction understanding that directly informs software solutions.</p>
                                </li>
                        </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mt-16">
                        <h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Technical Skills</h2>
                        <ul class="space-y-4">
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Languages:</strong> JavaScript, TypeScript, Python, SQL, Solidity
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Frontend:</strong> React, Astro, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion, Responsive Design
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express, Database Design & Optimization
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Web3:</strong> Hedera Network, Smart Contracts, Blockchain Development
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>3D/Graphics:</strong> Three.js, WebGL, Canvas, Spatial Visualization
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Geolocation:</strong> Mapping APIs, GPS Integration, Real-time Tracking
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <strong>Tools & Platforms:</strong> Git, Docker, REST APIs, GraphQL
                                </li>
                        </ul>
                </section>
        </div>

        <section class="mt-16">
                <h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Technologies & Frameworks</h2>
                <ul class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-2">
                        <li>
                                <a
                                        href="https://astro.build"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                        class="cactus-link inline-block"
                                >Astro</a>:
                                <p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">Build fast websites, faster. Perfect for building performant static and hybrid sites.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                                <a
                                        href="https://react.dev"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                        class="cactus-link inline-block"
                                >React</a>:
                                <p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">A JavaScript library for building interactive user interfaces with component-based architecture.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                                <a
                                        href="https://threejs.org"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                        class="cactus-link inline-block"
                                >Three.js</a>:
                                <p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">JavaScript 3D library for creating interactive 3D visualizations and spatial applications.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                                <a
                                        href="https://tailwindcss.com"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                        class="cactus-link inline-block"
                                >Tailwind CSS</a>:
                                <p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">Utility-first CSS framework for rapidly building modern, responsive designs.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                                <a
                                        href="https://www.postgresql.org/"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                        class="cactus-link inline-block"
                                >PostgreSQL</a>:
                                <p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">Powerful, open-source relational database for building scalable applications and inventory systems.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                                <a
                                        href="https://nodejs.org"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                        class="cactus-link inline-block"
                                >Node.js</a>:
                                <p class="inline-block sm:mt-2">JavaScript runtime for building scalable server-side applications and APIs.</p>
                        </li>
                </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-16">
                <h2 class="title mb-4 text-xl">Get In Touch</h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                        Interested in collaborating or learning more about my work? Feel free to reach out through any of my social channels or email me at <a class="hover:underline" href="mailto:matthieufelker@skiff.com">matthieufelker@skiff.com</a>.
                </p>
        </section>
</PageLayout>
